# **DaisyUI Reading Template (“Docs Shell”)**

This is a universal HTML template you can convert into a `docs_layout()` function the same way we did for the dashboard.

**Focus:**

* calming whitespace
* ideal for reading and contemplation
* clean typography
* scalable to tablets + desktop
* DaisyUI components only (no JS / no Next.js)

---

